    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/834733997837cc05b167542f7faa5cf6.poster.avif?t=1766268551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/834733997837cc05b167542f7faa5cf6.webm?t=1766268551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/834733997837cc05b167542f7faa5cf6.mp4?t=1766268551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《剑湾奇旅》是一款奇幻类cRPG游戏，灵感来自于由无限引擎打造的《博德之门1》、《冰风谷》等经典游戏。<br><br>你将扮演一名孤独的冒险者，踏上前往新德拉古尼亚这片未知之地的旅途。<br><br>在旅途中，一名垂死之人将一件奇特的遗物托付于你，而这也将为你开启一场奇幻冒险，一场乃至会威胁到你所熟知与热爱的一切的阴谋就此慢慢拉开帷幕。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/503977cf2462b01ac79f55fe6c268ecb.poster.avif?t=1766268551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/503977cf2462b01ac79f55fe6c268ecb.webm?t=1766268551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/503977cf2462b01ac79f55fe6c268ecb.mp4?t=1766268551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《剑湾奇旅》的核心特色包括：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/a924db2bf17dce8f44e5cf82ef5b5280.webp?t=1766268551\" width=10 height=10 /></span> 灵活的战斗引擎。在回合制战斗中以战术家的身份体验战斗，或使用实时暂停（RtWP）模式加快节奏；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/a924db2bf17dce8f44e5cf82ef5b5280.webp?t=1766268551\" width=10 height=10 /></span> 无类别的角色扮演系统：每种属性组合都会提供独特的游戏体验、各具特色的对话，以及新颖的任务解决方法；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/a924db2bf17dce8f44e5cf82ef5b5280.webp?t=1766268551\" width=10 height=10 /></span> 受经典启发但又不失现代感的用户界面，可进行大量自定义；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/a924db2bf17dce8f44e5cf82ef5b5280.webp?t=1766268551\" width=10 height=10 /></span> 广阔的非线性世界，充满了独特的NPC与奖励探索的多解性任务，总能提供不同的方法来满足任何角色构建；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/a924db2bf17dce8f44e5cf82ef5b5280.webp?t=1766268551\" width=10 height=10 /></span> 数十小时的探索，从宁静的小村庄到隐秘的古代庙宇、恐怖地窖、奇异地牢，以及异世界场地……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108180/extras/f41f7e283eacba6ef9c0a302b19705cf.avif?t=1766268551\" width=616 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >请将我们添加至您的愿望单！</h2><i>加入愿望单对我们游戏的知名度至关重要，同时也可以帮助我们确定应该优先考虑哪种语言的本地化。如果您想帮助我们将游戏<strong>翻译成您的语言</strong>，请务必考虑将我们添加至您的愿望单。</i>",
